<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" class="loan_product_table" width="100%"><tr valign="top">
<td class="loan_margin"></td>
<td id="prodInfo">
<h1>适用对象：</h1>
1、	生产经营达到一定规模的家庭农场主、专业大户；
2、	20周岁（含20周岁）至60周岁（含60周岁）之间，具有完全民事行为能力的自然人；
3、	具有当地户口或在当地连续居住一年以上；
4、	必须已婚（含离异、丧偶），家庭成员中有两名（含两名）以上的劳动力；

<h1>产品简介：</h1>
针对农民专业合作社法人、实际控制人、社员，额度最高可达1000万元，担保方式可为保证、抵质押和组合担保
<h1>产品额度：</h1>
额度最高可达50万元
<h1>产品利率：</h1>
基准利率上浮10%起
</td>
<td class="loan_margin"></td>
</tr>
</table>

<div class="form_button1" id="mybtn" onclick="doApply()"><div class="form_button_txt1">申请</div></div>
<script type = "text/javascript">

	function doApply() {
		
		if (prodId == null || prodId == undefined) {
			alert("获得产品失败,无法提交");
			return false;
		}
		var pid = "id=" + prodId;
		var price = "price_unit="+price_unit
		
		var jumpUrl = "./sumbit.html?" + pid +"&"+price;
		
		var doApply = document.getElementById("mybtn");
		myBtnClick(doApply,'#0091cb',jumpUrl);
		
	}

</script>
<br /><br />

</body>

<script type="text/javascript" src="../js/jquery-2.1.4.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
	var prodId;
	var price_unit;
	var bankMapArr = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("company_info"));
	var bankMap = new Map();
	bankMap.elements = bankMapArr;
	$(document).ready(function() {
		GetBankList();
    });
	
	//获取URL中的活动id参数
    function getUrlParam(paraName) {
        var reg = new RegExp("(^|&)" + paraName + "=([^&]*)(&|$)"); //构造一个含有目标参数的正则表达式对象
        var retStr = window.location.search.substr(1).match(reg);  //匹配目标参数
        var ret = unescape(retStr[2]);
        return ret;
    }
	
	function GetBankList() {
		$.post("/NewViliage/api/insurer/prodDetail?id=" + getUrlParam("prod_id"), function(data, textStatus) {debugger;
			if (textStatus == 'success' && data != null) {
				if (data.code==0) {
					value = data.result;
					if (value != null) {
						var bank = bankMap.get(value.ins_id);
						prodId = value.id;
						price_unit = value.price_unit;
						$("#loanName").html(value.ins_name);
						//$("#starImg").src = "/storage/" + value.prodIcon;
						$("#loanImg").attr("src","/storage/" + value.ins_icon);
						$("#bankImg").attr("src","/storage/" + bank.insurer_icon);
						$("#bankName").html(bank.insurer_name);
						$("#loanPrice").html(value.fitpeople);
						//$("#loanRate").html(value.rate);
						$("#prodInfo").html(value.ins_content);
					}
					
				}
			}
		}, 'json');
	}

</script>
</html>
